Tests
-------
Try to generate types and sql files for tests prior to test stage compile.
  Library classes should already be present in target/classes.
  Run exec plugin to generate sources into src/test/java/generated, using target/classes as classpath.
     generate-test-sources

GUI Query Spec Editor
---------------------
Ask for schema definition.
User chooses top table.
  Add TOS.

TOS ops
  Add/Remove field
  Change/customize output name for field.
  Add inline parent fields.
    (Starts new TOS editor to the side.)  
  Add referenced parent. 
    (Starts new TOS editor to the side.)  
  Add child collection
    (Starts new TOS editor to the side.)  

